# Trivy vulnerability allow-list for the CD image scan (cd.yml).
#
# Parity with the pip-audit allow-list in .github/workflows/ci.yml: the gate
# still fails on every NEW or FIXABLE CVE — only these documented advisories,
# which cannot be cleared without a separately-tracked major dependency bump,
# are suppressed. Re-audit and DELETE the corresponding lines when that bump
# lands.
#
# urllib3 — all fixed only in the urllib3 2.x line. urllib3 is capped <2.0.0
# (backend/requirements.txt) because kubernetes==28.1.0 has not been validated
# against the 2.x major; forcing it risks the in-cluster KubeVirt client that
# drives every migration. Lifts with the kubernetes 28->35 bump (tracked).
# Mirrors the same CVE set already accepted by pip-audit in ci.yml.
CVE-2025-50181
CVE-2025-66418
CVE-2025-66471
CVE-2026-21441
CVE-2026-44431
